  "3215050": {
    "name": "Surviving Mars: Relaunched",
    "steam_appid": 3215050,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i><strong>红色星球已焕然一新，再次体验激动人心的首次登陆，探索全新的秘密。</strong></i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎回家！这款屡获殊荣的科幻城市营造游戏经过复刻，现在内容更丰富，更引人入胜。你的任务是在火星上殖民并坚持存活。你需要探索、建造基础设施、迎接人类殖民地居民并实现长期稳定。有新的挑战要克服，新的战略要规划，只是现在游戏的画面感已得到升级，更适合新世代的探索者。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将再次开始执行创造欣欣向荣的火星定居点这项任务，而你需要的是稳定的资源与氧气供给、数十年的训练、应对沙尘暴的经验……以及保持好奇心，以查明凭空出现的黑色立方体的用途。只需要精心打扮一番，这个地方就能变成美丽的家园！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>《Surviving Mars: Relaunched》</i>将呈现来自Haemimont Games的这款殖民地管理游戏本体、所有资料片、大到主要扩展内容，小到皮肤和无线电台的全方位的改良与重制、以及全新的火星议会更新。升级过的画面以及更新过的用户界面将给老玩家呈现终极的《Surviving Mars》体验，同时为新手指挥官提供理想的发射点。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >准备好了吗？火星等待着你。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215050/extras/e8dc7ad4e72cc88058efe9e25e00e805.avif?t=1762794022\" width=780 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215050/extras/504f9948919d4acbaa5ab20605e49c02.poster.avif?t=1762794022\" width=780 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215050/extras/504f9948919d4acbaa5ab20605e49c02.webm?t=1762794022\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215050/extras/504f9948919d4acbaa5ab20605e49c02.mp4?t=1762794022\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >全新的火星议会将带来原版中前所未见且内容丰富的游戏终局挑战。通过法律来塑造火星社会。平衡你殖民地居民的需要与诉求，维持和平，并为火星发展长期计划，其中包括最终实现从地球独立！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215050/extras/a2298e1396503edce1d4a3cd6e80ca6e.avif?t=1762794022\" width=780 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215050/extras/761636ff389a36ef5580b9404914469f.poster.avif?t=1762794022\" width=780 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215050/extras/761636ff389a36ef5580b9404914469f.webm?t=1762794022\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215050/extras/761636ff389a36ef5580b9404914469f.mp4?t=1762794022\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在一颗不适合人类生存的行星上营造欣欣向荣的殖民地可谓困难重重。建造生命供给系统、电力供应网、穹顶和供应链，还要维持其正常运转，因为在一颗没有氧气的星球上发生停电就大事不妙了。你也并不孤单。重制版自带“<i>Space Race</i>”资料片，其他赞助者是你的竞争对手，他们会资助对手殖民地，给为了资源和火星未来而奋斗的你施加更大压力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215050/extras/97a8bd5b1052d442f0573a8371da7cd7.avif?t=1762794022\" width=780 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215050/extras/1856bfa10ca2621c0497c45e50a97ff3.poster.avif?t=1762794022\" width=780 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215050/extras/1856bfa10ca2621c0497c45e50a97ff3.webm?t=1762794022\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215050/extras/1856bfa10ca2621c0497c45e50a97ff3.mp4?t=1762794022\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >维持关键资源（如氧气、水资源、电力和食物）的平衡，以保障你殖民地居民的生存。无人机负责建造和维护你的基础设施，而得到更新的“<i>Martian Express</i>”新增了列车，能长途运输居民和物资。每位殖民地居民都有自己的需要和行为，巧妙管理对其生存至关重要。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215050/extras/b6ecc5f6ca9a8841be35152777f6d0b7.avif?t=1762794022\" width=780 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215050/extras/4e446a96bc40abcac90ed8eac90f949a.poster.avif?t=1762794022\" width=780 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215050/extras/4e446a96bc40abcac90ed8eac90f949a.webm?t=1762794022\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215050/extras/4e446a96bc40abcac90ed8eac90f949a.mp4?t=1762794022\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过具有深度的研究系统解锁新建筑、生产方式以及关键升级，以此来让你的殖民地更上一层楼。不要局限于火星地表，而要“<i>Below&amp;Beyond</i>”，探索突破性技术、资源和隐藏的秘密。我们随机化了地图、各个赞助者和不可预测的谜团，每次游玩都能带来新的挑战，你的每个决定都能塑造你在火星上求生与发展的故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215050/extras/a52e42453ea32047d064f53726ead16c.avif?t=1762794022\" width=780 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215050/extras/83481f0fdc48ae0b5661dbc58cdd8b96.poster.avif?t=1762794022\" width=780 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215050/extras/83481f0fdc48ae0b5661dbc58cdd8b96.webm?t=1762794022\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215050/extras/83481f0fdc48ae0b5661dbc58cdd8b96.mp4?t=1762794022\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >地球化不再是遥不可及的梦想，而是你的下一项挑战。该版本自带“<i>Green Planet</i>”资料片，你将把火星改造成一颗更适合居住的星球。随着环境的变化，你还能通过“<i>Project Laika</i>”让第一批动物登上火星，在你的殖民地居民的陪伴下茁壮成长。火星未来的重点不仅仅是生存，更是打造出一颗自给自足、生机勃勃的星球。</p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语<strong>*</strong>, 法语, 德语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 波兰语, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 俄语, 简体中文, 土耳其语<br><strong>*</strong>具有完全音频支持的语言",
